<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about">
    <h2>About Nishpaksh Samajh</h2>
    <p>
        Nishpaksh Samajh is a visionary framework that rejects mental hierarchy, ideological manipulation, and competitive ego-systems.  
        It embraces <strong>neutral consciousness, universal equality, and nature-integrated living</strong> as foundational values.
    </p>
    <p><strong>Core Mission:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>To free the human mind from jealousy, comparison and dominance</li>
        <li>To reconnect humanity with nature — not as a resource, but as a living parent</li>
        <li>To promote equality among all beings — human and non-human alike</li>
        <li>To build a future (Yatharth Yug) where love, compassion, and unbiased awareness prevail</li>
    </ul>
</section>

